ref=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nnb1665702671748.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nnb1665702671748.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nnb1665702671748.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nnb1665702671748\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the logo screen and the Uniface application are launched in\n    parallel or in sequence.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__topic_d144491e1_d144492e1_d144493e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__p_d144494e1_d144495e1_d144496e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">LogoSynch</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__section_rjy_wkc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d882765e68\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Arguments</strong></h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__ul_uzq_xkc_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__li_d50390e1_d50391e1_d50392e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>—the Uniface application is\n          lauched at the same time as the logo window is started. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__li_d50393e1_d50394e1_d50395e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>—the startup logo is displayed\n          first, followed by the Uniface application. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__section_nmg_zkc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d882765e88\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__table_w2853ab1b5b5b3_w2854ab1b5b5_w2855ab1b5_w2856ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> off </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> File Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ila1665702671184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ila1665702671184.html\" title=\"The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.\">[application]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__section_rry_1lc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d882765e132\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The time that the logo is displayed is determined by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">LogoTime</span>\n        setting. Thus if <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">LogoSynch</span> is set <code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>, the Uniface\n        application will not start until this time has elapsed and the logo window has closed.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"nnb1665702671748__note_w2857ab1b5b7b5_w2858ab1b5b7_w2859ab1b5_w2860ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Set\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">LogoSynchon</span> if Uniface appears to hang or crash when the startup logo\n        (splash screen) is enabled.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lco1665702671609.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Logo</a><p>Specifies the name of an image file to be used as the application splash screen logo. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lgk1665702671677.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>LogoTime</a><p>Specifies the time, in seconds, that the splash screen logo is displayed. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530337\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530337\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "LogoSynch Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines whether the logo screen and the Uniface application are launched in parallel or in sequence. LogoSynch { = } off | on Arguments off —the Uniface application is lauched at the same time as the logo window is started. on —the startup logo is displayed first, followed by the Uniface application. Defaults Default value: off File Section: [application] Description The time that the logo is displayed is determined by the LogoTime setting. Thus if LogoSynch is set on , the Uniface application will not start until this time has elapsed and the logo window has closed. Note: Set LogoSynchon if Uniface appears to hang or crash when the startup logo (splash screen) is enabled. Related Links Logo Specifies the name of an image file to be used as the application splash screen logo. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE. LogoTime Specifies the time, in seconds, that the splash screen logo is displayed. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}